---

# Expiration Engine

engine.js

Calculate:

```javascript
remainingDays =
expireDate - today
```

Status

```
>5 days

SAFE
Mint Green

3~5 days

WARNING
Amber

<=2 days

URGENT
Apple Red

<0

EXPIRED
```

Sort priority:

```
EXPIRED

↓

URGENT

↓

WARNING

↓

SAFE

↓

COMPLETED
```

